=== 2026-03-15 15:15 — SQLite fingerprint cache and data directory ===
- Added FingerprintCache (IFingerprintCache) backed by SQLite with WAL mode
  - Freshness check by file_size + last_modified
  - uint[] fingerprints serialized as little-endian BLOB via Buffer.BlockCopy
  - Prune method for batch-deleting entries whose files no longer exist
  - ToRelativePath helper for portable forward-slash relative paths
- Added AppConfig record (MediaRoot, DataDir) registered as DI singleton
- Added Microsoft.Data.Sqlite 9.0.3 NuGet dependency
- Program.cs: parse DATA_DIR (env > CLI > ./data default), register cache + config
- Worker.cs: accepts AppConfig and IFingerprintCache (wired for next step)
- docker-compose.yml: added /data volume mount and DATA_DIR env var
- Dockerfile: added VOLUME /data
- secrets/example.env: documented DATA_DIR
- Files created: src/AppConfig.cs, src/FingerprintCache.cs
- Files modified: src/Program.cs, src/Worker.cs, src/MediaSkipDetector.csproj,
  Dockerfile, docker-compose.yml, secrets/example.env
