=== 2026-03-15 22:00 — End credits detection ===
- Added credits detection using reversed fingerprint analysis:
  - Migration 004: fingerprint_type column on fingerprint_cache, PK now
    (relative_path, fingerprint_type) supporting both INTRO and CREDITS
  - Migration 005: metadata table with invalidate_skip_before timestamp —
    forces reprocessing of all directories when credits support is added
  - DirectoryScanner: treats .skip.json older than invalidate_skip_before as stale
  - AppConfig: added FfmpegPath, CreditsFingerprintSeconds (300),
    MinCreditsDuration (15), MaxCreditsDuration (300)
  - FpcalcService.RunTail(): gets duration via ffprobe, extracts tail audio
    via ffmpeg to temp WAV, fingerprints with fpcalc. Auto-detects
    ffmpeg/ffprobe on PATH or via FFMPEG_PATH env var.
  - IntroAnalysisService.AnalyzeCredits(): reverses fingerprints, runs pairwise
    comparison (same algorithm as intros), converts reversed timestamps to
    absolute positions, merges END_CREDITS into existing .skip.json files
  - Worker runs credits as second pass after intro analysis. Gracefully
    skipped when ffmpeg unavailable.
  - ScanMetrics: added CreditsFingerprinted, CreditsFingerprintErrors,
    CreditsDetected counters
  - Status page: shows ffmpeg availability, credits fingerprinting stats,
    credits detection counts in history table
  - Dockerfile: added ffmpeg to apk add
  - docs/TUNING.md: documented FFMPEG_PATH and credits tuning parameters
  - README.md: documented ffmpeg as development prerequisite, updated
    .skip.json example to show both INTRO and END_CREDITS entries
- Verified on real library:
  - Wheel of Time S02: credits in 8/8 episodes (6 comparisons)
  - Xena S06: credits in 22/22 episodes (17 comparisons)
  - invalidate_skip_before forced full reprocessing (108 dirs, 0 up to date)
